This method checks if the other enchantment is an arrow-based enchantment (such as `EnchantmentArrowDamage`, `EnchantmentArrowFire`, or `EnchantmentArrowInfinite`) and returns false if it is. Otherwise, it calls the super implementation to check if the enchantment can be applied together with other enchantments.

